    "description": "<i><strong>&quot;Let's cut to the heart of the matter: You're dead.&quot;</strong></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182140/extras/b801739c01f1be9d03187382e02cbbda.poster.avif?t=1771254542\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182140/extras/b801739c01f1be9d03187382e02cbbda.webm?t=1771254542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >An otherworldly experience.</h2><br>As a damned spirit, navigate through 7 unique worlds, each containing 5 levels of puzzles, platforming, and perforating hazards.<br>Place down your Spirit Gate, and return to it on a whim to navigate the increasingly labyrinthine platforming challenges.<br>Possess the humanoid and the formerly human; become a scarecrow, and scare crows (to death)!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A haunting tale of discovery and redemption.</h2><br>An amnesiac spirit begins her new life facing Izanami, the goddess of death. Though she is spared from the eternal flames of Hell, she has been chosen by Izanami to undertake a series of brain-bending trials!<br>Who is this spirit, and why is she not in the heavens where she thinks she ought to belong?<br>A hellish ordeal awaits, but does a satisfying answer lie at the journey's end?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master every level, and claim your rewards.</h2><br>Each of the 35 levels contains a photobook scrap. Take the extra steps to collect them all, and you might be in for a surprise.<br>In the meantime, every level grades you on your speed; can <i>you</i> capture the coveted S Rank on every level?<br>Every scrap and S Rank obtained adds a new item to your damned spirit's wardrobe; be the best, and look good doing it!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 35 intense levels of platforming action!<br></li><li> 7 beautiful, hand-crafted worlds, including Izanami's Palace, Ne-no-Kuni and Mt. Fuji!<br></li><li> A ranking system to show off your mastery of the game!<br></li><li> A compelling narrative and engaging characters!<br></li><li> Steam Achievements!<br></li><li> Getting reprimanded by the heavens for killing too many crows!</li></ul>",
